re is from a stale test import of an internal utility package moved in 3.1.x.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"For 3.1.0, do not import org.codehaus.janino.util.iterator.*; iterator utilities moved to org.codehaus.commons.compiler.util.iterator.* in commons-compiler, which is already a transitive dependency of janino. Prefer public Janino APIs such as ExpressionEvaluator, ScriptEvaluator, ClassBodyEvaluator, SimpleCompiler, and Compiler for coverage.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Tests that exercise runtime code generation may hit Native Image dynamic class loading limitations; existing Janino tests already account for this pattern.\",\n    \"Avoid relying on old internal org.codehaus.janino.util.* packages when updating tests from 3.0.x to 3.1.x.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_039d24173b58bfaa016a4278c396108193806bd0d5a707d6b4\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1121, "output": 749, "cacheRead": 18432, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 20302, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782741176407, "responseId": "resp_039d24173b58bfaa016a4278b8ce8c8193b5686048485888e9"}}
